Company Overview of Focused Investors LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Focused Investors LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, state and municipal government entities, employee benefit plans, foundations, and endowments. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm primarily invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It primarily invests in value stocks of large-cap companies. The firm employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up approach to make its investments. Focused Investors LLC was founded in 2006 and is based in Beverly Hills, California.


9777 Wilshire BoulevardSuite 910Beverly Hills, CA 90212-1902United StatesFounded in 2006



Phone: 310-734-1200

Fax: 310-734-1201

www.focusedinvestors.com/







