Focused Investors LLC Buys CBS Corp, Sells McDonald's Corp, International Business Machines Corp, Microsoft CorpJuly 19, 2017 |  About: 
CBS  +0%
MCD  +0%
IBM  +0%
MSFT  +0%
MMM  +0%
JPM  +0%
BBBY  +0% 



Beverly Hills, CA, based Investment company Focused Investors LLC buys CBS Corp, sells McDonald's Corp, International Business Machines Corp, Microsoft Corp, 3M Co, JPMorgan Chase during the 3-months ended 2017-06-30, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Focused Investors LLC. As of 2017-06-30, Focused Investors LLC owns 23 stocks with a total value of $2.4 billion.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: CBS, Reduced Positions: MCD, IBM, MSFT, ZBH, MMM, CVS, JNJ, ANTM, AXP, WMT, Sold Out: BBBY, Warning! GuruFocus has detected 6 Warning Signs with CBS. Click here to check it out. 
CBS 30-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of CBSPeter Lynch Chart of CBSFor the details of Focused Investors LLC's stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=Focused+Investors+LLCThese are the top 5 holdings of Focused Investors LLCZimmer Biomet Holdings Inc (ZBH) - 1,156,700 shares, 6.31% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 19.3%Anthem Inc (ANTM) - 762,400 shares, 6.09% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 19.31%CVS Health Corp (CVS) - 1,712,300 shares, 5.85% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 19.26%American Express Co (AXP) - 1,627,400 shares, 5.83% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 18.23%Johnson & Johnson (JNJ) - 1,035,600 shares, 5.82% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 19.46%New Purchase: CBS Corp (CBS)Focused Investors LLC initiated holdings in  CBS Corp.  The purchase prices were between $60.34 and $69.51, with an estimated average price of $64.07.   The stock is now traded at around $65.08. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 3.08%. The holdings were 1,136,200 shares as of 2017-06-30. Sold Out: Bed Bath & Beyond Inc (BBBY)Focused Investors LLC sold out the holdings in  Bed Bath & Beyond Inc.  The sale prices were between $29.65 and $39.93, with an estimated average price of $36.29. Reduced: McDonald's Corp (MCD)Focused Investors LLC reduced to the holdings in  McDonald's Corp by 33.58%.  The sale prices were between $129.29 and $154.8, with an estimated average price of $144.15.   The stock is now traded at around $153.54. 						The impact to the portfolio due to this sale was -1.88%. Focused Investors LLC still held 793,000 shares as of 2017-06-30. Reduced: International Business Machines Corp (IBM)Focused Investors LLC reduced to the holdings in  International Business Machines Corp by 38.28%.  The sale prices were between $150.37 and $174.52, with an estimated average price of $158.02.   The stock is now traded at around $147.02. 						The impact to the portfolio due to this sale was -1.85%. Focused Investors LLC still held 473,200 shares as of 2017-06-30. Reduced: Microsoft Corp (MSFT)Focused Investors LLC reduced to the holdings in  Microsoft Corp by 26.04%.  The sale prices were between $64.95 and $72.52, with an estimated average price of $68.6.   The stock is now traded at around $73.93. 						The impact to the portfolio due to this sale was -1.43%. Focused Investors LLC still held 1,707,400 shares as of 2017-06-30. Reduced: 3M Co (MMM)Focused Investors LLC reduced to the holdings in  3M Co by 33.1%.  The sale prices were between $188.65 and $213.36, with an estimated average price of $199.74.   The stock is now traded at around $212.06. 						The impact to the portfolio due to this sale was -1.18%. Focused Investors LLC still held 343,400 shares as of 2017-06-30. Reduced: JPMorgan Chase & Co (JPM)Focused Investors LLC reduced to the holdings in  JPMorgan Chase & Co by 20.39%.  The sale prices were between $82.15 and $91.15, with an estimated average price of $86.23.   The stock is now traded at around $91.19. 						The impact to the portfolio due to this sale was -0.88%. Focused Investors LLC still held 1,079,100 shares as of 2017-06-30. Here is the complete portfolio of Focused Investors LLC. Also check out:
